profile:
Derek Vittie is a native of Pelham Ontario and has been a professional sealer since 2015. He has sealed over 650 driveways.


Driveway/patio sealing is both easy and cost effective method to protect and prolong the life of your driveway. Asphalt surfaces are particularly susceptible to daily wear and tear from weather and especially from automobile traffic. The grade of asphalt commonly used today on driveways is even more so. Driveway sealing at regular intervals gives your driveway the additional protection it needs to last longer and resist deterioration.
specialities: Concrete Sealing, Ashpahlt Sealing, Ashphalt Sealing and Repair, Polymeric Sand Application, Interlock Sealing,Interlock Sanding, Pressure Washing, Paving Maintenance, Snow Removal.
